ht to vote, when their gullibility is being actively weaponized in a desperate attempt to stop the SAVE Act.\n\nWhen they can\u2019t be even bothered to ask ChatGPT or Grok if it\u2019s true, and just believe what they\u2019re told on their right to vote, it just goes to show they can\u2019t be trusted in general to make an informed decision on just about anything else. \n\nI don\u2019t intrinsically hate women, but I\u2019d be stupid to ignore this disturbing growing trend that seems biologically unique to the majority of women.\n\nEDIT: I apologize to the based women here who this opinion might piss off. Congratulations on being the exception. But you also have to come to terms with the reality that, you are the exception to most women, and I wish to God that you weren\u2019t.", "author": "Redpilled2Depression", "created": 1770864654558, "profile_picture": "WGyogqEwEUTb", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "CleanUpPhillyTrump24", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "\ud83d\udea8 HOT TAKE: The fact that there\u2019s going to be women who actually believe that the SAVE Act will remove their ability to vote, when 5 minutes of research would prove otherwise\u2026", "last_comment_created": 1770870142085, "content": "<p>\u2026only further validates my growing belief that women shouldn\u2019t have the right to vote, when their gullibility is being actively weaponized in a desperate attempt to stop the SAVE Act.</p>\n<p>When they can\u2019t be even bothered to ask ChatGPT or Grok if it\u2019s true, and just believe what they\u2019re told on their right to vote, it just goes to show they can\u2019t be trusted in general to make an informed decision on just about anything else.</p>\n<p>I don\u2019t intrinsically hate women, but I\u2019d be stupid to ignore this disturbing growing trend that seems biologically unique to the majority of women.</p>\n<p>EDIT: I apologize to the based women here who this opinion might piss off. Congratulations on being the exception. But you also have to come to terms with the reality that, you are the exception to most women, and I wish to God that you weren\u2019t.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": true, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 4, "score_up": 57, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASFhQGDZA", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 554, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8412818, "raw_content": "", "author": "Trick", "created": 1770820070956, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "lifeisahologram", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASFhQGDZA.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/PXvARvRBJEuN.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/neO7lkyU1GJb0jBB.png", "width": 622, "content-type": "png", "height": 255}], "blurhash": "U5RfkB00=wiv?H8_Dha0_3RjRi%ME1_NyDNb", "full_resolution": [255, 622]}, "title": "This", "last_comment_created": 1770854683366, "content": "", "score_down": 5, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 10, "score_up": 559, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text"